@koji-1009 I haven't digested your message in detail, but I would like to just comment on this:

> In Flutter 3.27, the HTML renderer is no longer available.

The HTML renderer is still available in 3.27. The only thing that's changed is you get a warning when you pass `--web-renderer=html`. The complete removal is scheduled for the first release in 2025.

